pol:32018L2001 a pol:PolicyDocument ;
    pol:hasArticle pol:EU_32018L2001_Title_0_Chapter_0_Section_0_Article_14 .

pol:EU_32018L2001_Title_0_Chapter_0_Section_0_Article_14 a pol:PolicyArticle ;
    pol:fullText """article 14
capacity increases
for the purposes of article 9(2) and point (b) of article 11(2), units of energy from renewable sources imputable to an increase in the capacity of an installation shall be treated as if they were produced by a separate installation becoming operational at the moment at which the increase of capacity occurred."""^^xsd:string .

