pol:EU_32018L2001_Title_0_Chapter_0_Section_0_Article_37 a pol:PolicyArticle ;
    pol:addresses pol:Member_States ;
    pol:fullText """article 37
repeal
directive 2009/28/ec, as amended by the directives listed in part a of annex x, is repealed with effect from 1 july 2021, without prejudice to the obligations of the member states relating to the time-limits for the transposition into national law of the directives set out in part b of annex x and without prejudice to the obligations of member states in 2020 as laid down in article 3(1) and set out in part a of annex i to directive 2009/28/ec.
references to the repealed directive shall be construed as references to this directive and shall be read in accordance with the correlation table set out in annex xi."""^^xsd:string ;
    pol:specifies_compliance_time pol:EU_32018L2001_Title_0_Chapter_0_Section_0_Article_37_TimeCompliance_2 ;
    pol:specifies_in_effect_time pol:EU_32018L2001_Title_0_Chapter_0_Section_0_Article_37_TimeInEffect_1 .

