        <http://eurovoc.europa.eu/6049> ;
    pol:fullText """article 11
committee
1.   the commission shall be assisted by the statistical programme committee.
2.   where reference is made to this paragraph, article 5a(1) to (4) and article 7 of decision 1999/468/ec shall apply, having regard to the provisions of article 8 thereof.
3.   where reference is made to this paragraph articles 5 and 7 of decision 1999/468/ec shall apply, having regard to the provisions of article 8 thereof.
the period provided for in article 5(6) of decision 1999/468/ec shall be three months."""^^xsd:string ;
