member states shall lay down the rules on penalties applicable in case of non-compliance with the national provisions adopted pursuant to articles 7 to 11 and article 18(3) and shall take the necessary measures to ensure that they are implemented. the penalties provided for shall be effective, proportionate and dissuasive. member states shall notify those provisions to the commission by 5 june 2014 and shall notify it without delay of any subsequent amendment affecting them."""^^xsd:string ;
