    pol:fullText """article 13
assessment of the integrated national energy and climate plans
on the basis of the integrated national energy and climate plans and their updates as notified pursuant to articles 3 and 14, the commission shall assess, in particular, whether:
(a)
the objectives, targets and contributions are sufficient for the collective achievement of the energy union objectives and, for the first ten-year period in particular, the targets of the union's 2030 climate and energy framework;
(b)
the plans comply with requirements of articles 3 to 12 and member states have taken due account of the commission recommendations issued pursuant to article 34."""^^xsd:string ;
